---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const title = "Condo HOA tradeoff vs SFH repairs";
const description = "The real cost tradeoff: dues + rules vs maintenance + reserves.";
---

<BaseLayout title={`${title} | BRIK`} description={description}>
  <section style="padding:28px 0 10px">
    <h2 style="font-size:30px;margin:0 0 10px;letter-spacing:-.4px">{title}</h2>
    <p style="margin:0 0 18px;color:var(--muted);max-width:80ch">{description}</p>

    <div class="card">
      <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Scenario</h3>
      <p style="margin:0;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.7">
        You’re torn: condo convenience vs single-family control. You want clarity beyond vibes.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div style="display:grid;gap:14px;grid-template-columns:repeat(12,1fr);margin-top:14px">
      <div class="card" style="grid-column:span 6">
        <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">Condo math & checks</h3>
        <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.7">
          <li>HOA covers what, exactly?</li>
          <li>Reserves healthy? (future repairs funded?)</li>
          <li>Rental rules (caps/approval)?</li>
          <li>Special assessment history?</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="grid-column:span 6">
        <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">SFH math & checks</h3>
        <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.7">
          <li>Roof/HVAC age and life left</li>
          <li>Plumbing + electrical condition</li>
          <li>Foundation/drainage red flags</li>
          <li>Build a repair reserve fund</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-top:14px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03)">
      <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px">BRIK takeaway</h3>
      <p style="margin:0;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;line-height:1.7">
        Condos trade repairs for rules and shared risk. SFHs trade rules for personal responsibility.
        The “right” answer depends on your cash reserves, lifestyle, and how much uncertainty you can carry.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:12px">
        <a class="pill" href="/case-studies">Back to Case Studies</a>
        <a class="pill primary" href="/intake">Submit Intake</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
